<HL>
   `Coming to America'
   Suit Comes to This:
   $58 Million Gap
   ---
   Sum Underscores Divergencee
   In Claims of Buchwald
   And Paramount Pictures
   ----
   By David J. Jefferson
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
